</TD>
<TD>
<P>Patients' Mean Scores on the Children's Depression Inventory.<BR/>I = before: 10.00 (SD 7.02) versus after: 6.69 (SD 5.65), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>I = after: 6.69 (SD 5.65) versus C = 7.75 (SD 6.47), P = not significant.<BR/>
