<TD>
<P>Patients' mean Scores on the Deasy-Spinetta Behavioral Questionnaire (Teachers' ratings)<BR/>I = before: 23.42 (SD 6.81) versus after: 26.46 (SD 5.85), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>I = after: 26.46 (SD 5.85) versus C = 18.87 (SD 8.33), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>
