</TD>
<TD>
<P>Patients' Mean Scores on the Perceived Competence Scale for Children.<BR/>Cognitive: I = before: 2.62 (SD 0.75) versus after: 2.87 (SD 0.72), P &lt; 0.05. I = after: 2.87 (SD 0.72) versus C = 2.66 (SD 0.63), P = not significant.<BR/>Social: I = before: 2.85 (SD 0.79) versus after: 3.23 (SD 0.60), P &lt; 0.05.<BR/>I = after: 3.23 (SD 0.60) versus C = 2.96 (SD 0.62), P &lt; 0.05.<BR/>Physical: I = before: 2.43 (SD 0.74) versus after: 2.82 (SD 0.67), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>I = after: 2.82 (SD 0.67) versus C = 2.84 (SD 0.66), P = not signifcant.<BR/>General: I = before: 2.88 (SD 0.59) versus after: 3.34 (SD 0.49), P = not significant.<BR/>I = after: 3.34 (SD 0.49) versus C = 2.96 (SD 0.56), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>
</P>
</TD>
<TD>
<P>Teacher's Rating of Child's Actual Competencies<BR/>Cognitive: I = before: 3.16 (SD 0.99) versus after: 3.22 (SD 0.89), P = not signficant.<BR/>I = before: 3.16 (SD 0.99) versus C = 2.32 (SD 0.90), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>I = after: 3.22 (SD 0.89) vs. C = 2.32 (SD 0.90), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>Social: I = before: 3.33 (SD 0.66) versus after: 3.11 (SD 0.67), P = not signficant.<BR/>I = after: 3.11 (SD 0.67) vs. C = 2.79 (SD 3.33), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>Physical: I = before: 2.73 (SD 1.20) versus after: 2.78 (SD 0.74), P = not significant.<BR/>I = after: 2.78 (SD 0.74) vs. C = 2.35 (SD 0.85), P &lt; 0.05.<BR/>General: I = before: 3.46 (SD 0.52) versus after: 3.48 (SD 0.49), P = not significant.<BR/>I = after: 3.48 (SD 0.49) vs. C = 2.91 (SD 0.83), P &lt; 0.01.<BR/>
<BR/>
<BR/>
</P>
</TD>
<TD>
<P>Absences and grades:<BR/>No statistically significant differences were observed between groups on absences or grades.<BR/>Mean Days absent*<BR/>Year before diagnosis: I (n = 29) = 9.85 (SD 3.43, range 0 to 40) versus C = 11.57 (SD 10.08, range 0 to 38).<BR/>Year of the diagnosis: I (n = 35) = 53.88 (SD 33.24, range 3 to 137) versus C = 46.00 (SD 17.92, range 4 to 72).<BR/>Year after the diagnosis: I (n = 32) = 39.28 (SD 32.71, range 0 to 138) versus C = 33.33 (SD 19.37, range 6 to 86).<BR/>
