</TD>
<TD>
<P>Heart rate: Intervention group participants had significantly lower mean heart rates (beats per minute) from baseline to simulated radiation therapy during the total treatment than modified control group participants: I = 112.3 (SD 3.0) to 106.2 (SD 3.2) versus C = 105.1 (SD 2.3) to 108.4 (SD 2.8), F = 4.11, P &lt; 0.05).</P>
</TD>
